          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <a href="/projects/moltworker/" class="text-xs bg-biolum/10 text-biolum px-3 py-1 rounded-full hover:bg-biolum/20 transition-colors">View Moltworker</a>
            <a href="/projects/aionui/" class="text-xs bg-biolum/10 text-biolum px-3 py-1 rounded-full hover:bg-biolum/20 transition-colors">View AionUi</a>
            <a href="/compare/moltworker-vs-aionui/" class="text-xs bg-white/5 text-gray-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">Moltworker vs AionUi</a>
